urchase order, selected products/services on a purchase order, or purchase orders for a specific customer in their entirety or on a selection basis. The report format allows for the inclusion of \"reasons\" relative to the status of the purchase order(s). This transaction set may also be used to update the supplier's scheduled shipment or delivery date(s). This transaction set can result from either an inquiry (via the Order Status Inquiry transaction [869] or a prearranged schedule agreed to by the trading partners. (DM #: 360388)","TransactionSet":[{"Id":"ST"},{"Id":"BSR"},{"Id":"NTE","Min":0,"Max":100},{"Id":"REF","Min":0,"Max":12},{"Id":"N1Loop1","Loop":[{"Id":"N1"},{"Id":"N2","Min":0,"Max":2},{"Id":"N3","Min":0},{"Id":"N4","Min":0},{"Id":"REF","Min":0,"Max":12},{"Id":"PER","Min":0,"Max":3}],"Min":0,"Max":200},{"Id":"DTM","Min":0,"Max":10},{"Id":"HLLoop1","Loop":[{"Id":"HL"},{"Id":"PRF","Min":0},{"Id":"ISRLoop1","Loop":[{"Id":"ISR"},{"Id":"QTY","Min":0,"Max":4}],"Min":0,"Max":104},{"Id":"REF","Min":0,"Max":12},{"Id":"PER","Min":0,"Max":3},{"Id":"DTM","Min":0,"Max":10},{"Id":"N1Loop2","Loop":[{"Id":"N1"},{"Id":"N2","Min":0,"Max":2},{"Id":"N3","Min":0},{"Id":"N4","Min":0},{"Id":"REF","Min":0,"Max":12},{"Id":"PER","Min":0,"Max":3}],"Min":0,"Max":200},{"Id":"PO1Loop1","Loop":[{"Id":"PO1"},{"Id":"SLN","Min":0,"Max":100},{"Id":"PO3","Min":0},{"Id":"PID","Min":0,"Max":1000},{"Id":"MEA","Min":0,"Max":40},{"Id":"PKG","Min":0,"Max":25},{"Id":"ISRLoop2","Loop":[{"Id":"ISR"},{"Id":"QTY","Min":0,"Max":4},{"Id":"DTM","Min":0,"Max":10},{"Id":"N1","Min":0},{"Id":"TD1","Min":0},{"Id":"TD5","Min":0},{"Id":"TD3","Min":0},{"Id":"TD4","Min":0},{"Id":"REF","Min":0,"Max":12}],"Min":0,"Max":104}],"Min":0,"Max":1000}],"Max":1000},{"Id":"CTT"},{"Id":"SE"}]},"002002_997":{"Release":"002002","DocumentType":"997","name":"Functional Acknowledgment","Introduction":"The purpose of this standard is to define the control structures for a set of acknowledgments to indicate the results of the syntactical analysis of the electronically encoded documents. The encoded documents are the transaction sets, which are grouped in functional groups, used in defining transactions for business data interchange. This standard does not cover the semantic meaning of the information encoded in the transaction sets.","TransactionSet":[{"Id":"ST"},{"Id":"AK1"},{"Id":"AK2Loop1","Loop":[{"Id":"AK2"},{"Id":"AK3Loop1","Loop":[{"Id":"AK3"},{"Id":"AK4","Min":0,"Max":99}],"Min":0,"Max":"unbounded"},{"Id":"AK5","Min":0}],"Min":0,"Max":"unbounded"},{"Id":"AK9"},{"Id":"SE"}]}}}
